log.content: I would like you to create an svg image of a sunset through the mountains. Make sure the result is visible in index.html

function.name: create_file
function.arguments:
{"filename":"index.html","content":"<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><title>Sunset over Mountains</title></head>
<body>
<svg width="800" height="400" viewBox="0 0 800 400">
  <defs>
    <linearGradient id="skyGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="0%" y2="100%">
      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#FF9966"/>
      <stop offset="50%" stop-color="#FFD700"/>
      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#663399"/>
    </linearGradient>
  </defs>
  <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#skyGradient)"/>
  
  <!-- Front Mountain -->
  <polygon points="0,300 200,150 400,300" fill="#333"/>
  
  <!-- Middle Mountain -->
  <polygon points="400,300 600,175 800,300" fill="#555"/>
  
  <!-- Back Mountain Range -->
  <polygon points="0,400 800,400 800,300 0,300" fill="#222"/>
</svg>
</body>
</html>"}
